[28C[3A]0;⠂ Claude Code[28D[3B[4A[48;2;55;55;55m[38;2;80;80;80m❯ [38;2;255;255;255mI'm building a web app called RightNow@MIT. MIT students rate tonight's dining hall quality in real time so others [39m   [1B  [38;2;255;255;255mknow if it's worth walking over.[39m                                                                                      [1B  [38;2;255;255;255mScope for V1 tonight:[39m                                                                                                 [1B                                                                                                                        [49m
[48;2;55;55;55m  [38;2;255;255;255m5 halls: Maseeh, McCormick, Next, Baker, Simmons[39m                                                                      [49m
[48;2;55;55;55m  [38;2;255;255;255mEach shows tonight's aggregate star rating (1-5) and rating count[39m                                                     [49m
[48;2;55;55;55m  [38;2;255;255;255mTap a hall → submit a 1-5 rating + optional short comment[39m                                                             [49m
[48;2;55;55;55m  [38;2;255;255;255mNo auth — anonymous ratings, but rate-limit one rating per hall per device per day via localStorage[39m                   [49m
[48;2;55;55;55m  [38;2;255;255;255mRatings are "tonight only" — filter to ratings from the last 6 hours when showing aggregate[39m                           [49m
[48;2;55;55;55m  [38;2;255;255;255mMobile-first UI (students will use this walking to dinner)[39m                                                            [49m
[48;2;55;55;55m                                                                                                                        [49m
